    <abstract>
      <t>This document defines the "ANAME" DNS RR type, to provide similar functionality to CNAME, but only for type A and AAAA queries. Unlike CNAME, an ANAME can coexist with other record types. The ANAME RR allows zone owners to make an apex domain name into an alias in a standards compliant manner.</t>
